
Files in this directory

*.h files----------
  threads.h -- used by all programs that use pthreads
  sem.h -- semaphores using pthreads
  monitor.h -- monitors using pthreads

*.c Files---------
  thread_test.c  -- testing thread creation
  lock_test.c  -- testing locking and unlocking
  sem_test.c  -- testing semaphores
  prod_cons_s.c  -- producer/consumer using semaphores
  read_write_s.c  -- readers and writeres using semaphores
  prod_cons_m.c  -- producer/consumer using monitors
  read_write_m.c -- readers and writeres using monitors

other files-------
           
  race-c.c -- a race condition using Linux "clone"
  race-p.c -- a race condition using pthreads



